thread.title: BRIEF-Beijing Highlander Digital Technology sees FY 2017 net profit to up 11 pct to 41 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Beijing Highlander Digital Technology sees FY 2017 net profit to up 11 pct to 41 pct

organizations.name: beijing highlander digital technology co ltd

text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Beijing Highlander Digital Technology Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 11 percent to 41 percent, or to be 91 million yuan to 115.6 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 82.0 million yuan
* Says growth of core businesses as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/dARf88
